RESOURCE.STRING: Starting EFC Actuator Override Test

Initial Conditions 
1. Engine stopped 
2. Key Switch on 
Steps 
1. Select Start 
2. Select desired Commanded Actuator Position to open or close actuator 
3. Monitor Fuel Pump Actuator Position parameter 
Additional Information 
1. Test runs for a maximum of 60 seconds 
2. If required, select Stop to end the test early
EFC Actuator Override Test
This test can be used to validate the EFC Actuator operation by allowing the user to open and close the actuator.
This test is not supported by the current calibration.
